             was indicted for <rs id="t17850629-40-off189" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850629-40-off189" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850629-40-off189" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17850629-40-cd190" type="crimeDate">28th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850629-40-off189 t17850629-40-cd190"></join>, one pair of metal shoe buckles, value 2 s. two pair of cotton stockings, value 2 s. one handkerchief, value 3 s. two remnants of muslin, value 1 s. a cap, value 1 s. 6 d. a silk purse, value 6 d. one piece of thread edging, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17850629-40-victim377" type="victimName">
