                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850629-40-victim379 t17850629-40-viclabel191"></join>; and a silver milk pot, value 10 s. one silver table spoon, value 6 s. two tea-spoons, value 6 s. a pair of sugar tongs, value 10 s. a ladle, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17850629-40-victim379" type="victimName">
